---
// src/components/FAQ.astro
---
<section id="faq" class="py-32 relative bg-slate-50">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 tracking-tight text-display">Questions?</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-500">No tech jargon, promised.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="ui-card rounded-xl p-6 bg-white cursor-pointer hover:border-slate-300">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Do I really own the website?</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">Yes, 100%. Unlike some agencies that "rent" you a website, once you pay, it is yours forever. You own the domain, the code, and the content.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="ui-card rounded-xl p-6 bg-white cursor-pointer hover:border-slate-300">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">What if I need to change a phone number or price later?</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">For small changes, just text us. We handle minor updates for free for the first year. For larger changes, we have affordable maintenance packs, or we can teach you how to do it.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="ui-card rounded-xl p-6 bg-white cursor-pointer hover:border-slate-300">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">How long does it take to build?</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">Because we don't use clunky templates, we move fast. Most "Starter" and "Local Growth" sites are live within 7-10 days after we get your details.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>